$ v$instance

gh|oracle-patterns|/Installed/dynamic-performance-views/instance/columns.sql||

{ instance_role

  `instance_role` can be used to determine if an instance is an active instance (=primary instance) or a secondary instance (in a → http://www.adp-gmbh.ch/ora/data_guard/index.html[standby environment])

}
{ version

  → development/databases/Oracle/installed/packages/dbms/utility/index[dbms_utility.db_version] can be used to retrieve the same version as the field version in v$instance.

}

sa:
